  body "gu|કેમ છે}}? {{qualifier|informal}}\n* Haitian Creole: {{t-needed|ht}}\n* Hawaiian: {{t|haw|pehea ʻoe}}?\n* Hebrew: {{t|he|מה שלומך|alt=?מה שלומך|tr=ma shlomkha?}} (''singular male''), (ma shlomekh?) "
