  body " Tupi: {{t|tpw|ereîkobépe}}\n* Palauan: [[ke ua ngerang]]?\n* Pashto: {{t|ps|څنگه يې؟}}\n* Persian:\n*: Iranian Persian: {{qualifier|familiar and colloquial}} {{t|fa-ira|حالِت چِطورِه؟|tr=hâlet četor-"
